{"tid":829930,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[iPhone撚入] 記憶體成日不足","createTime":"2018-09-20T23:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T15:18:01.000Z","uid":4880,"like":217,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"cb4bd30a141f894d051c9313743a67c3c4aa22a8","tid":829930,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T23:43:21.000Z","msg":"我用緊部64GB嘅iPhone 6s<br />\n用到咁上下佢就開始話low memory<br />\n本身都冇為意，諗住剷走啲冇用嘅apps同相就當problem fixed啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當呢個情況持續嘅時候，我手痕睇睇佢storage，想話搵邊個app又大舊又冇點用可以剷<br />\n拉到底時見到有舊叫system嘅野佔成24GB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/073738_2f5a90cc6cb8f2b8a71797818acd728a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F073738_2f5a90cc6cb8f2b8a71797818acd728a.png&h=1f6e62b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問咁多位ching呢個情況是咪正常？如果唔正常，有冇辦法可以自己搞幫佢瘦身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外想換新機嘅話iPhone XS Max好定Note9好？用左咁多年iPhone我有少少心郁想轉會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : XS Max<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : Note9"},{"pid":"f17b1f706d8663146b6b8efa2808e849576a5e9c","tid":829930,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T23:59:41.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446c2c2df0525e8cf6bc9dae811a18e7169122f1","tid":829930,"uid":32577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T00:03:19.000Z","msg":"提你換機呀"},{"pid":"3c24169abd297d668f469f91f79443f78bec4b60","tid":829930,"uid":112416,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T00:07:08.000Z